《'''黑洞頻率'''》（{{lang-en|''Frequency''}}）是一部改編自2000年由{{link-en|奎葛利·霍里|Gregory Hoblit}}執導、{{link-en|陶比·艾默李奇|Toby Emmerich}}編劇的[[黑洞頻率|同名電影]]，並由{{link-en|傑若米·卡佛|Jeremy Carver}}開發電視版，於2016年10月5日在[[CW電視網|The CW]]開播的[[美國|美國]]電視影集。<ref name="TheCWPremiereDates">{{cite web|url=http://tvbythenumbers.zap2it.com/2016/06/17/the-cw-fall-tv-2016-premiere-dates-the-flash-and-no-tomorrow-kick-off-october-rollout/|title=The CW fall TV 2016 premiere dates: ‘The Flash’ and ‘No Tomorrow’ kick off October rollout|work=[[TV_by_the_Numbers|TV by the Numbers]]|date=2016-06-17|accessdate=2016-06-17|archive-date=2016-09-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160914154718/http://tvbythenumbers.zap2it.com/2016/06/17/the-cw-fall-tv-2016-premiere-dates-the-flash-and-no-tomorrow-kick-off-october-rollout/|dead-url=yes}}</ref>

2017年5月8日，The CW宣布取消本劇。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/live-feed/frequency-no-tomorrow-canceled-at-cw-1001320|title='Frequency', 'No Tomorrow' Canceled at The CW|last=Goldberg|first=Lesley|last2=Stanhope|first2=Kate|work=[[荷里活報道|好萊塢報導]]|date=2017-05-08|accessdate=2017-05-08|archive-date=2018-08-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180808171456/https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/live-feed/frequency-no-tomorrow-canceled-at-cw-1001320|dead-url=no}}</ref>

== 故事 ==
2016年，紐約警署警探芮米·蘇利文意外利用父親的[[業餘無線電|無線電]]和20年前的父親法蘭克·蘇利文聯繫上，並試圖改變父親死亡的事實。在挽救父親的性命後，改變過去的芮米卻因此意外引發蝴蝶效應，導致她所熟悉的一切將通通改變，包括愛情甚至是至親。現在，她必須和父親聯手，以解決一樁未能破案的連環殺人事件，並修正一切。<ref name="pickups">{{cite news |last=Andreeva |first=Nellie |url=http://deadline.com/2016/05/riverdale-frequency-no-tomorrow-picked-up-to-series-by-the-cw-1201754618/ |title=‘Riverdale’, ‘Frequency’ & ‘No Tomorrow’ Picked Up To Series By The CW |work=[[Deadline.com|Deadline.com]] |date=2016-05-12 |accessdate=2016-05-13 |archive-date=2017-10-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171013172543/http://deadline.com/2016/05/riverdale-frequency-no-tomorrow-picked-up-to-series-by-the-cw-1201754618/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>

