=== 開發 ===
2014年11月13日，[[全國廣播公司|NBC]]宣布開發《[[黑洞頻率|黑洞頻率]]》電視版，並由《[[邪惡力量|超自然檔案]]》[[節目統籌|主理人]]{{link-en|傑若米·卡佛|Jeremy Carver}}執筆，並和原電影版編劇{{link-en|陶比·艾默李奇|Toby Emmerich}}及約翰·里卡德、[[林暐|林暐]]與珍妮佛·葛華茲共同擔任執行製作。<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/live-feed/nbc-plots-frequency-reboot-supernatural-748851|title=NBC Plots 'Frequency' Reboot With 'Supernatural' Boss (Exclusive)|author=Lesley Goldberg|work=好萊塢報導|date=2014-11-13|accessdate=2016-10-16|archive-date=2016-12-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161201061154/http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/live-feed/nbc-plots-frequency-reboot-supernatural-748851|dead-url=no}}</ref>

2015年8月11日，宣布本劇正式由[[CW電視網|The CW]]接手。<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/live-feed/friday-13th-tv-cw-814736|title=CW Prepping 'Friday the 13th' for TV|author=Lesley Goldberg|work=好萊塢報導|date=2015-08-11|accessdate=2016-10-16|archive-date=2016-06-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160622183551/http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/live-feed/friday-13th-tv-cw-814736|dead-url=no}}</ref>

2016年1月29日，The CW宣布預訂本劇試播集。<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://deadline.com/2016/01/kevin-williamson-paranormal-project-frequency-remake-cw-pilot-orders-1201693259/|title=Kevin Williamson’s Paranormal Project, ‘Frequency’ Remake Get CW Pilot Orders|author=Nellie Andreeva|work=Deadline.com|date=2016-01-29|accessdate=2016-10-16|archive-date=2016-10-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161016170343/http://deadline.com/2016/01/kevin-williamson-paranormal-project-frequency-remake-cw-pilot-orders-1201693259/|dead-url=no}}</ref>5月12日，本劇獲The CW系列預訂。<ref name="pickups"/>

